OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy this evening and overnight with
OL,7,Fthe chance of some rain or drizzle at
OL,8,Ftimes, this most persistent across
OL,9,Fparts of Cumbria. A blustery and mild
OL,10,Fnight with the southwesterly winds
OL,11,Fpreventing temperatures from falling
OL,12,Fvery much.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FA blustery and rather wet
OL,15,Fday to come with heavier spells of
OL,16,Frain at times. Windy around some
OL,17,Fcoasts and hills. Not as mild, but
OL,18,Ftemperature still above average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
