OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FWindy
OL,6,Fand often wet on Friday, drier later.
OL,7,FDrier and brighter on Saturday, then
OL,8,Fwet and windy on Sunday with heavy and
OL,9,Fpersistent rain in places.
OL,10,FTemperatures often above average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
